<br>
Once the agro list is full up with lower level raiders then each 53+ person can get in one shot before being banished. One sword swing from a tank is pretty useless so we don't generally bother with them, but we do use people that can get in one big nuke or heal. We also have casters bind and gate back in for a 2nd and 3rd whack hehe. Paladins can get in one group heal or lay hands and shadowknights might be able to get close enough to harm touch. We will generally use our casters to debuff. <p><b>
